      "text": "The big thing to understand is that guilds were basically proto unions built upon two major factors:\n\n1. Quality of craft (aka, don't make crap that breaks!)\n2. Fair wages for work\n\nLiterally the foundation of:\n\n- organized labor\n- democratic governance\n- safety regulation\n- the middle class"
